data.description: This property has everything you need for your Florida dream house. POOL home on a freshwater canal, go FISHING in your backyard! New roof in 2022 and Impact windows installed in 2020 you will have some of the best insurance savings around. Beat the high interest rates and take advantage of this whole home solar powered package! With an average electric bill of only $175/month versus a $300+/month bill from LCEC! This spectacular home has the perfect amount of space for hosting your family get togethers, updated kitchen appliances and great views out to your outdoor living area. Pool installed in 2010 and all pool equipment has been replaced within the last couple of years. Every feature of this property from the giant kitchen to the spacious master bedroom and master bath will make you feel right at home!
